542
00:33:39,380 --> 00:33:41,360
A further destination?

543
00:33:41,780 --> 00:33:43,880
Where is it?

544
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:45,200
Isn't it Beijing?

545
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:48,200
How can there be a farther destination than Beijing?

546
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:49,744
Of course.

547
00:33:49,744 --> 00:33:54,932
