00:35:45,840 --> 00:35:49,432
Did your dad say anything harsh this time?

576
00:35:49,432 --> 00:35:51,020
Nope.

577
00:35:51,020 --> 00:35:54,124
Didn't you hear him tell me to do my job well?

578
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:58,436
That's rare.

579
00:36:08,120 --> 00:36:10,160
Chairman Xie, want a cup of coffee?

580
00:36:10,160 --> 00:36:12,608
No, thanks. I'll just have this.

581
00:36:13,080 --> 00:36:14,080
Where's Hongdou?

