645
00:39:44,120 --> 00:39:46,100
<i>All right. Sort this out at home.</i>

646
00:39:46,100 --> 00:39:49,140
<i>- No!
- Discuss this at the village committee then.
- I'm not going.</i>

647
00:39:49,140 --> 00:39:51,760
